====================INPUT=====================
//WAP TO REVERSE A POSITIVE INTEGER 

#include <stdio.h>

int main() {
   int p,q,sum=0;

   printf("enter any number to be reversed: ");
   scanf("%d",&p);
   
   
   while(p>=1){
       q=p%10;
       p=p/10;
       sum=sum*10+q;
   }
   
   p=sum;
   printf("\n\nafter reversing: %d",p);

   
   return 0;
}
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

=================================OUTPUT===================
enter any number to be reversed: 123456


after reversing: 654321

=== Code Execution Successful ===


enter any number to be reversed: 6789


after reversing: 9876

=== Code Execution Successful ===

